117→     * A thread must only be in one state at a time
118→     * The expected state transitions with the following defined states is:
119→     *
120→     * <pre>
121→     *                 +-------------+
122→     *          +<---- | Created (0) |
123→     *          |      +-----+-------+
124→     *          |            |
125→     *          |            v
126→     *          |      +-----+-------+
127→     *          +<---- | Starting (1)|----->+
128→     *          |      +-----+-------+      |
129→     *          |                           |
130→     *          |            +<----------+  |
131→     *          |            |           |  |
132→     *          |            v           |  |
133→     *          |      +-----+-------+   |  |
134→     *          +<---- | Partitions  | --+  |
135→     *          |      | Revoked (2) | <----+
136→     *          |      +-----+-------+      |
137→     *          |           |  ^            |
138→     *          |           v  |            |
139→     *          |      +-----+-------+      |
140→     *          +<---- | Partitions  |      |
141→     *          |      | Assigned (3)| <----+
142→     *          |      +-----+-------+      |
143→     *          |            |              |
144→     *          |            +<----------+  |
145→     *          |            |           |  |
146→     *          |            v           |  |
147→     *          |      +-----+-------+   |  |
148→     *          |      |             | --+  |
149→     *          |      | Running (4) | ---->+
150→     *          |      +-----+-------+
151→     *          |            |
152→     *          |            v
153→     *          |      +-----+-------+
154→     *          +----> | Pending     |
155→     *                 | Shutdown (5)|
156→     *                 +-----+-------+
157→     *                       |
158→     *                       v
159→     *                 +-----+-------+
160→     *                 | Dead (6)    |
161→     *                 +-------------+
